<solution id="fs-idp40726272">
<para id="fs-idm45305280"><emphasis effect="italics">C</emphasis>|<emphasis effect="italics">L</emphasis> means, given the person chosen is a Latino Californian, the person is a registered voter who prefers life in prison without parole for a person convicted of first degree murder.</para></solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="exercise5"><problem id="id13153551">
